00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:40,719
He's one of Junior Chi's people,
just open it and show him.

544
00:42:40,719 --> 00:42:42,239
What?

545
00:42:42,239 --> 00:42:45,800
No matter who, I won't open it.

546
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,919
Wasting my time.

547
00:42:49,519 --> 00:42:51,319
Gang.

548
00:42:55,239 --> 00:42:57,079
Come on, pry it open.

549
00:42:57,079 --> 00:42:58,400
Don't open it.

550
00:42:58,400 --> 00:43:00,199
