00:43:29,280 --> 00:43:30,960
It's you again.

558
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:34,960
What do you want?
Whatever I do, you're always there.

559
00:43:34,960 --> 00:43:36,320
What are you doing?

560
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:38,319
This is Mr. Chi from the Warehouse Department.

561
00:43:39,320 --> 00:43:42,360
What? I don't care which department you're from.

562
00:43:42,360 --> 00:43:44,519
Compensate me.

563
00:43:44,519 --> 00:43:45,519
How much?

564
00:43:45,519 --> 00:43:47,319
500 yuan.

565
00:43:49,159 --> 00:43:52,679
Gang, pay him 5,000.

566
00:43:52,679 --> 00:43:55,479
Come, come over here.

567
00:44:10,639 --> 00:44:12,559
Chi Cheng.

568
00:44:12,559 --> 00:44:14,519
- She is really beautiful.
- Yes.

569
00:44:14,519 --> 00:44:16,319
Really beautiful.

570
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,920
