574
00:44:33,599 --> 00:44:35,760
Do you miss me?

575
00:44:37,480 --> 00:44:38,760
Let's go.

576
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:41,680
Okay, let's go.

577
00:44:46,880 --> 00:44:52,079
<i>No wonder he's been against me all along,
causing me to mess up several jobs.</i>

578
00:44:52,079 --> 00:44:56,959
